title: [Gyldemar Forest, Crooked Path]
description: The path ends near a gigantic oak tree.  Its upper branches sway in the wind, while the lower branches remain still, shielded by the other trees.  A woodpecker occasionally attacks the oak vainly, the old wood hard like stone.

The path ends near a gigantic oak tree, a sinister shape in the night darkness and moonlight.  Its upper branches sway in the wind, while the lower branches remain still, shielded by the other trees.  A woodpecker occasionally attacks the oak vainly, the old wood hard like stone.
